#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.2:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Mettāvagga"
msgstr "1. Love"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 2. Paññāsutta → ādibrahmacariyapaññāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Paññāsutta"
msgstr "2. Wisdom"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, hetū aṭṭha paccayā ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are eight causes and reasons that lead to acquiring the "
"wisdom fundamental to the spiritual life, and to its increase, growth, "
"development, and fulfillment once it has been acquired."

msgctxt "an8.2:1.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.2:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satthāraṃ upanissāya viharati aññataraṃ vā "
"garuṭṭhāniyaṃ sabrahmacāriṃ, yatthassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ "
"hoti pemañca gāravo ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant lives relying on the Teacher or a spiritual companion "
"in a teacher’s role. And they set up a keen sense of conscience and prudence "
"for them, with warmth and respect."

msgctxt "an8.2:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo hetu paṭhamo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the first cause."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.152"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:2.1"
msgid ""
"So taṃ satthāraṃ upanissāya viharanto aññataraṃ vā garuṭṭhāniyaṃ "
"sabrahmacāriṃ, yatthassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti pemañca "
"gāravo ca, te kālena kālaṃ upasaṅkamitvā paripucchati paripañhati:"
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant lives relying on the Teacher or a spiritual companion in a "
"teacher’s role—with a keen sense of conscience and prudence for them, with "
"warmth and respect—from time to time they go and ask them questions:"

msgctxt "an8.2:2.2"
msgid "‘idaṃ, bhante, kathaṃ; imassa ko attho’ti?"
msgstr "‘Why, sir, does it say this? What does that mean?’"

msgctxt "an8.2:2.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa te āyasmanto avivaṭañceva vivaranti, anuttānīkatañca uttānīkaronti, "
"anekavihitesu ca kaṅkhāṭhāniyesu dhammesu kaṅkhaṃ paṭivinodenti."
msgstr ""
"Those venerables clarify what is unclear, reveal what is obscure, and dispel "
"doubt regarding the many doubtful matters."

msgctxt "an8.2:2.4"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo hetu dutiyo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the second cause."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:3.1"
msgid ""
"So taṃ dhammaṃ sutvā dvayena vūpakāsena sampādeti—kāyavūpakāsena ca "
"cittavūpakāsena ca."
msgstr ""
"After hearing that teaching they perfect withdrawal of both body and mind."

msgctxt "an8.2:3.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo hetu tatiyo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the third cause."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:4.1"
msgid ""
"Sīlavā hoti, pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati ācāragocarasampanno "
"aṇumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvī, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant is ethical, restrained in the monastic code, and has appropriate "
"behavior and means of collecting alms. Seeing danger in the slightest flaw, "
"they keep the rules they’ve undertaken."

msgctxt "an8.2:4.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho hetu catuttho paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the fourth cause."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ → satthā sabyañjanā (si) | sātthaṃ savyañjanaṃ (pts1)
#. VAR: dhātā → dhatā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an8.2:5.1"
msgid ""
"Bahussuto hoti sutadharo sutasannicayo. Ye te dhammā ādikalyāṇā "
"majjhekalyāṇā pariyosānakalyāṇā sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ "
"parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ abhivadanti, tathārūpāssa dhammā bahussutā honti "
"dhātā vacasā paricitā manasānupekkhitā diṭṭhiyā suppaṭividdhā."
msgstr ""
"They’re very learned, remembering and keeping what they’ve learned. These "
"teachings are good in the beginning, good in the middle, and good in the "
"end, meaningful and well-phrased, describing a spiritual practice that’s "
"entirely full and pure. They are very learned in such teachings, remembering "
"them, reinforcing them by recitation, mentally scrutinizing them, and "
"comprehending them theoretically."

msgctxt "an8.2:5.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, pañcamo hetu pañcamo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the fifth cause."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.153"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:6.1"
msgid ""
"Āraddhavīriyo viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo anikkhittadhuro kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"They live with energy roused up for giving up unskillful qualities and "
"gaining skillful qualities. They’re strong, firmly applied, not slacking off "
"when it comes to developing skillful qualities."

msgctxt "an8.2:6.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, chaṭṭho hetu chaṭṭho paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the sixth cause."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:7.1"
msgid "Saṅghagato kho pana anānākathiko hoti atiracchānakathiko."
msgstr "When in the Saṅgha they don’t engage in motley talk or unworthy talk."

msgctxt "an8.2:7.2"
msgid ""
"Sāmaṃ vā dhammaṃ bhāsati paraṃ vā ajjhesati ariyaṃ vā tuṇhībhāvaṃ "
"nātimaññati."
msgstr ""
"Either they talk on Dhamma, or they invite someone else to do so, or they "
"respect noble silence."

msgctxt "an8.2:7.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, sattamo hetu sattamo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the seventh cause."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:8.1"
msgid "Pañcasu kho pana upādānakkhandhesu udayabbayānupassī viharati:"
msgstr "They meditate observing rise and fall in the five grasping aggregates."

msgctxt "an8.2:8.2"
msgid "‘iti rūpaṃ, iti rūpassa samudayo, iti rūpassa atthaṅgamo;"
msgstr "‘Such is form, such is the origin of form, such is the ending of form."

msgctxt "an8.2:8.3"
msgid "iti vedanā, iti vedanāya samudayo, iti vedanāya atthaṅgamo;"
msgstr ""
"Such is feeling, such is the origin of feeling, such is the ending of "
"feeling."

msgctxt "an8.2:8.4"
msgid "iti saññā … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Such is perception, such is the origin of perception, such is the ending of "
"perception."

msgctxt "an8.2:8.5"
msgid "iti saṅkhārā …"
msgstr ""
"Such are choices, such is the origin of choices, such is the ending of "
"choices."

msgctxt "an8.2:8.6"
msgid "iti viññāṇaṃ, iti viññāṇassa samudayo, iti viññāṇassa atthaṅgamo’ti."
msgstr ""
"Such is consciousness, such is the origin of consciousness, such is the "
"ending of consciousness.’"

msgctxt "an8.2:8.7"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, aṭṭhamo hetu aṭṭhamo paccayo ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattati."
msgstr "This is the eighth cause."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:9.1"
msgid "Tamenaṃ sabrahmacārī evaṃ sambhāventi:"
msgstr "Their spiritual companions esteem them:"

msgctxt "an8.2:9.2"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā satthāraṃ upanissāya viharati aññataraṃ vā garuṭṭhāniyaṃ "
"sabrahmacāriṃ, yatthassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ hoti pemañca "
"gāravo ca."
msgstr ""
"‘This venerable lives relying on the Teacher or a spiritual companion in a "
"teacher’s role. They set up a keen sense of conscience and prudence for "
"them, with warmth and respect."

msgctxt "an8.2:9.3"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr "Clearly this venerable knows and sees.’"

#. VAR: piyattāya garuttāya → piyatāya garutāya (s1-3)
msgctxt "an8.2:9.4"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(1)"
msgstr "This quality leads to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.154"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:10.1"
msgid ""
"‘Taṃ kho panāyamāyasmā satthāraṃ upanissāya viharanto aññataraṃ vā "
"garuṭṭhāniyaṃ sabrahmacāriṃ, yatthassa tibbaṃ hirottappaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ "
"hoti pemañca gāravo ca, te kālena kālaṃ upasaṅkamitvā paripucchati "
"paripañhati:"
msgstr ""
"‘This venerable lives relying on the Teacher or a spiritual companion in a "
"teacher’s role, and from time to time they go and ask them questions …"

msgctxt "an8.2:10.2"
msgid "“idaṃ, bhante, kathaṃ; imassa ko attho”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:10.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa te āyasmanto avivaṭañceva vivaranti, anuttānīkatañca uttānīkaronti, "
"anekavihitesu ca kaṅkhāṭhāniyesu dhammesu kaṅkhaṃ paṭivinodenti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:10.4"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr "Clearly this venerable knows and sees.’"

msgctxt "an8.2:10.5"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(2)"
msgstr "This quality also leads to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:11.1"
msgid ""
"‘Taṃ kho panāyamāyasmā dhammaṃ sutvā dvayena vūpakāsena sampādeti—"
"kāyavūpakāsena ca cittavūpakāsena ca."
msgstr ""
"‘After hearing that teaching they perfect withdrawal of both body and mind."

msgctxt "an8.2:11.2"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr "Clearly this venerable knows and sees.’"

msgctxt "an8.2:11.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(3)"
msgstr "This quality also leads to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:12.1"
msgid ""
"‘Sīlavā kho panāyamāyasmā pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharati "
"ācāragocarasampanno aṇumattesu vajjesu bhayadassāvī, samādāya sikkhati "
"sikkhāpadesu."
msgstr "‘This venerable is ethical …"

msgctxt "an8.2:12.2"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr "Clearly this venerable knows and sees.’"

msgctxt "an8.2:12.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(4)"
msgstr "This quality also leads to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:13.1"
msgid ""
"‘Bahussuto kho panāyamāyasmā sutadharo sutasannicayo. Ye te dhammā "
"ādikalyāṇā majjhekalyāṇā pariyosānakalyāṇā sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ "
"kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ abhivadanti, tathārūpāssa dhammā "
"bahussutā honti dhātā vacasā paricitā manasānupekkhitā diṭṭhiyā "
"suppaṭividdhā."
msgstr ""
"‘This venerable is very learned, remembering and keeping what they’ve "
"learned. …"

msgctxt "an8.2:13.2"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr "Clearly this venerable knows and sees.’"

msgctxt "an8.2:13.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(5)"
msgstr "This quality also leads to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:14.1"
msgid ""
"‘Āraddhavīriyo kho panāyamāyasmā viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya, "
"kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo anikkhittadhuro "
"kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr "‘This venerable lives with energy roused up …"

msgctxt "an8.2:14.2"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr "Clearly this venerable knows and sees.’"

msgctxt "an8.2:14.3"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(6)"
msgstr "This quality also leads to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.155"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:15.1"
msgid "‘Saṅghagato kho panāyamāyasmā anānākathiko hoti atiracchānakathiko."
msgstr "‘When in the Saṅgha they don’t engage in motley talk or unworthy talk."

msgctxt "an8.2:15.2"
msgid ""
"Sāmaṃ vā dhammaṃ bhāsati paraṃ vā ajjhesati ariyaṃ vā tuṇhībhāvaṃ "
"nātimaññati."
msgstr ""
"Either they talk on Dhamma, or they invite someone else to do so, or they "
"respect noble silence."

msgctxt "an8.2:15.3"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr "Clearly this venerable knows and sees.’"

msgctxt "an8.2:15.4"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(7)"
msgstr "This quality also leads to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:16.1"
msgid ""
"‘Pañcasu kho panāyamāyasmā upādānakkhandhesu udayabbayānupassī viharati—"
msgstr ""
"‘They meditate observing rise and fall in the five grasping aggregates. …"

msgctxt "an8.2:16.2"
msgid "iti rūpaṃ, iti rūpassa samudayo, iti rūpassa atthaṅgamo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.3"
msgid "iti vedanā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.4"
msgid "iti saññā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.5"
msgid "iti saṅkhārā …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.6"
msgid "iti viññāṇaṃ, iti viññāṇassa samudayo, iti viññāṇassa atthaṅgamoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an8.2:16.7"
msgid "Addhā ayamāyasmā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passatī’ti."
msgstr "Clearly this venerable knows and sees.’"

msgctxt "an8.2:16.8"
msgid ""
"Ayampi dhammo piyattāya garuttāya bhāvanāya sāmaññāya ekībhāvāya saṃvattati. "
"(8)"
msgstr "This quality also leads to warmth, respect, esteem, harmony, and unity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "an8.2:17.1"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha hetū aṭṭha paccayā ādibrahmacariyikāya paññāya "
"appaṭiladdhāya paṭilābhāya, paṭiladdhāya bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāya bhāvanāya "
"pāripūriyā saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the eight causes and reasons that lead to acquiring the wisdom "
"fundamental to the spiritual life, and to its increase, growth, development, "
"and fulfillment once it has been acquired.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.2:17.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
